{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"7":"Fasting"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1683,"arabicnumber":1683,"text":"১/১৬৮৩। ‘আয়িশাহ্ (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। তিনি বলেন, নবী সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম রমযান মাসে চুমা দিতেন।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan Or Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":46}}]}